    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to evaluate whether Folrex, could improve the motor recovery of
      the upper extremity after stroke in comparison with placebo during 4 weeks of treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Periodical measures of the motor recovery, of the upper extremity, by Fugl-Meyer score, it
      will be done at the beginning, at fifth day and at month. Each value will be compare to
      evaluate whether the groups of patient improve.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
